================================================================================
2.  LICENSE-BOUND RECEIPTS (SCSL-1.0 §11)
================================================================================

    Every Receipt emitted by the Software (every JSON / CBOR / σ-binary
    artefact that records a kernel verdict) carries a cryptographic anchor
    to THIS LICENSE.  The reference SHA-256 of  LICENSE-SCSL-1.0.md  is
    pinned in       ./LICENSE.sha256

    Anyone may, at any time, verify that an emitted Receipt matches a
    Spektre-Labs-blessed Release of the Software by recomputing that hash:

        sha256sum  LICENSE-SCSL-1.0.md   # POSIX
        shasum -a 256  LICENSE-SCSL-1.0.md   # macOS

    A Receipt that does not carry a matching license_sha256 is
    admissible evidence of a SCSL §6 / §8 / §11 breach (see §11.4).

